Notes::::

Create new environment via
# pip install -r requirements.txt

Activate new environment
# source activate financial_instability

Refresh requirements file
# pip freeze >requirements.txt

Create new database
# python manage.py create_db

Delete database
# python manage.py destroy_db

web: uwsgi --http-socket :5000 --wsgi-file manage.py


Set up cron job like so to generate monster SP500 file
# crontab -e
<location_of_conda_env>/financial_instability/bin/python2.7 <location_of_project>/financial_instability/financial_instability_app/utils/generate_sp500_data.py
